Simplify SMS Messaging by Using DLT Templates in MobileConnect

Use Digital Ledger Technology (DLT) templates to ensure that you comply with the Telecoms Regulatory Authority of India (TRAI) regulations. Simplify your campaign process and reduce spam messages by using the templates for your messages in MobileConnect and Journey Builder.

How: Contact your Account Executive to enable this feature.
title: Simplify SMS Messaging with Digital Ledger Technology
